content.html: There is nothing wrong with compliments. There is everything wrong with sexual harassment. How do you know the difference? If you wouldn’t say it to a woman when she’s stood next to her 7ft heavily built father who’d punch your face in. Then it’s the latter, don’t say it.
content.value:
There is nothing wrong with compliments.

There is everything wrong with sexual harassment.

How do you know the difference?

If you wouldn’t say it to a woman when she’s stood next to her 7ft heavily built father who’d punch your face in. Then it’s the latter, don’t say it.
